            <scopecontent id="aspace_56ca807772508845b524a7a50dc37767">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Series II includes materials commemorating the life and career of William Pickens. Scrapbooks document his civic achievements, and ephemera from Yale College, Phi Beta Kappa, and other academic and cultural organizations and events document Pickens' academic and activist career.</p>
            </scopecontent>
            <arrangement id="aspace_60053c21783c4a622969dd034c59d160">
               <head>Arrangement</head>
               <p>Series II is arranged in no particular order.</p>
            </arrangement>
